arStrings.szText: Forgive my familiarity as I write. Harsh words better tell the tale of hard times.
Maybe the end of those times nears. Our leader, the archangel Tyrael, led us to this vault before setting off on a task of his own. Heâ€™s entrusted me to lead in his place.
A little more optimistic then Lorath usually is--this is written decades ago.
The rebirth of the Horadric Order is up to the few of us who remain.
